page.title: 05Brookmans Park Housing
page.content: All the houses in Brookmans Park are privatly owned.Most of the houses are detached and have their own large gardens.Four or five of the roads are private and most people use them for short cuts to the A1000.The gardens in Brookmans Park are well looked after with many expensive features. Most of the houses were built after the opening of the local railway station. Most of the houses have been designed differently.Many of them have had extensions added but unfortunately some of them do not fit in with the original design.
